===Head to the Exalting Sanctum and meet with Nannan{{subst:void|<!--202160202-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Exalting Sanctum|update|You thought the matter had come to an end for the time being, but then you receive a strange message from Zhongshan... There seems to be something else to this incident that you have been kept in the dark from. Go to Nannan and ask him about it.}}
{{Dialogue Start}}
:'''(Trailblazer):''' (What on earth is Zhongshan up to? Let me take a look at the cycrane stand.)

;(Talk to Nannan)
:'''Nannan:''' (Trailblazer)? What are you doing here?
:'''Nannan:''' Let me make this clear &mdash; You and your tutor better not think of persuading me into releasing some bizarre creatures this time...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Don't worry. Zhongshan is gone...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm here to collect a letter from her...
:'''Nannan:''' What? She left? Why did she, too, leave unannounced just like my three buddies?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Aren't they being punished?
:'''Nannan:''' I'm not sure what happened. I was told that they were either fined or imprisoned. I thought of visiting them to see how I could help.
:'''Nannan:''' But those at the Realm-Keeping Commission said they had been taken away on bail. They were nowhere to be seen, and they didn't reply to any of my messages. It was as though they had vanished into thin air.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} They unshackled the Unshackled.
::'''Nannan:''' Have they decided to leave the Unshackled behind and go away? Benna might do such a thing, but not Tonya or Heathmann.
::'''Nannan:''' Also, none of those who are close to them has seen them so far...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I don't think they would notify you before leaving.
::'''Nannan:''' It's possible, since they've always looked down on me.
::'''Nannan:''' However, none of those who are close to them have seen them either.
:'''Nannan:''' By the way, that friend of yours also left me a gift here. Let me see what it is...
:'''Nannan:''' A case of mineral water. Hehe, what a thoughtful young lady. Actually, when I met you two for the first time in Scalegorge Waterscape, my intuition already told me that you two weren't cut out for this releasing business.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...The first time you met us?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...Isn't she a member of the Unshackled?
:'''Nannan:''' Huh? Who told you she was one of us?
:'''Nannan:''' Isn't she your friend? We thought she was there to help you persuade us to let you join the Unshackled. Wasn't it the case? We didn't know her at all before she brought you here.
:'''(Trailblazer):''' (Who in the world is Zhongshan?)
{{Dialogue End}}

