===Chat with Nannan{{subst:void|<!--202160204-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Exalting Sanctum|update|The story is almost over, my friend. Is this story funny? If it is, then just make a laughing sound like "Aha!" If not... then remember to write that down in your feedback. I'll try to make you laugh next time.}}
{{Dialogue Start}}

;(Talk to Nannan)
:'''Nannan:''' What did Zhongshan say in the letter?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Tell the truth.)
::'''Nannan:''' I see... She "unshackled" the three of them? This is... baffling...
::'''Nannan:''' Well, it isn't entirely a bad thing. Now that the obsessed trio isn't here, the Unshackled will be off the radar of the Realm-Keeping Commission. It makes my life a lot easier.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Keep the truth a secret.)
::'''Nannan:''' She didn't say anything important? Alas... I thought she would at least explain the whole thing to you.
::'''Nannan:''' Well, this isn't entirely a bad thing. Now that the obsessed trio isn't here, The Unshackled will be off the radar of the Realm-Keeping Commission. It makes my life a lot easier.
:'''Nannan:''' Anyway, it might be some time before the Three Benevolent Ones come back... From now on, I'll be the only Benevolent One... Hmm... maybe it's time to think about the future of the Unshackled.
:'''Nannan:''' Please feel free to swing by and take part in our activities... Now that the Microscopic Faction is at the helm, there won't be anymore dangerous activities like releasing beasts.
{{Dialogue End}}

